## ✨ **Features**

✅ Simple & clean chat UI with **WhatsApp-like bubbles**  
✅ Live AI responses for travel queries  
✅ User **Login / Signup** system  
✅ Query **History** for each user  
✅ **Admin Dashboard** to manage users & all queries  
✅ **Twilio** integration — call & WhatsApp support  
✅ Mobile-friendly, responsive design

---

## ⚙️ **Tech Stack**

| Tech | Details |
|------|---------|
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js |
| **Frontend** | EJS, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap 5 |
| **Database** | MongoDB + Mongoose |
| **Messaging** | Twilio WhatsApp API |
| **AI API** | OpenAI / GPT integration (or your logic) |

